---
import SectionHeading from "./SectionHeading.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="scroll-animate">
      <SectionHeading
        label="About"
        title="A bit about me"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 scroll-animate">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground scroll-animate clip-reveal">
        I'm a Staff Software Engineer and frontend architect with 14+ years building scalable web applications, design systems, and component libraries across CRM, fintech, and SaaS platforms. I specialize in owning complex product surfaces end-to-end — from authoring architecture proposals to shipping production code at velocity.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground scroll-animate clip-reveal" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
        My approach centers on system-level thinking: building the right abstractions, establishing governance patterns, and creating tools that empower teams to ship faster without accumulating debt. I care deeply about the space between design and engineering — tokens, motion, layout, and the craft of translating design intent into production UI that feels exactly right.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground scroll-animate clip-reveal" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
        Currently championing AI-forward engineering practices and building design systems at scale. I believe the best work happens when engineering rigor meets design precision — and when teams have the right tools to move fast without breaking things.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
